Sylvia Kauders https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sylvia_Kauders 0 Sylvia Kauders (née Wolinsky; December 1, 1921 – May 5, 2016) was an American film, television, and theater actress known for numerous small but memorable roles on Broadway and in major motion pictures.
